creator: Safeco Insurance Company of America
descriptionHtml:
Insurance Simplified

Help is on the way

Take full control of your policy with our app features:

- Seamless biometrics login
- Contact your agent directly
- Review your coverages
- Access documents and ID cards
- Make payments
- File claims


Never get stranded: Help is on the way with Safeco Roadside Assistance.

Call Roadside Support, record information, and capture photos at the scene of an accident. The app keeps you informed about your claim at every step of the way.

- Tap to call for Roadside Assistant
- File a claim, upload photo of damages, and track claim status
- Search for auto repair shops, schedule a vehicle inspection, or request a rental vehicle
- View repair estimates, track your vehicle repairs and check on your payment status
- Get an auto repair estimate on eligible claims in 48 hours

descriptionShort: Safeco Mobile puts all your insurance needs right at your fingertips.
title: Safeco Mobile

creator: Safeco Insurance Company of America
descriptionHtml:
Download the improved Safeco mobile app for a comprehensive digital gateway to your insurance policy. Easily log in with fingerprint or facial recognition - then access your insurance ID cards with just one tap. Make your life easier and quickly manage the rest of your policy from anywhere, at any time. Download today!

We’re here for what you need

Easily take care of what’s important, and much more!
- Access auto insurance ID cards and all policy documents
- Pay your bill with credit/debit cards and manage automatic payments
- Learn about your current auto and property coverages and additional options available to you
- Get notified about policy documents ready to be signed
- Easily contact your Safeco agent for assistance, including making changes to your policy

Help when you need it most

When you’re broken down or need to file or move your claim forward, the app can help!
- Tap to call for emergency Roadside Assistance
- File and manage your claims, and contact your claims adjuster
- Take and upload pictures of damage or use our guided photo capture experience to get a repair estimate quickly
- Search for auto repairs shops, schedule a damage review, or request a rental vehicle
- View repair estimates, track your vehicle repairs, and check on your payment status

descriptionHtml:
Get the Safeco mobile app, your one-stop insurance resource. Log in fast and securely with touch or face recognition. Access ID cards with one touch. Manage your policy or claim from anywhere, at any time. You can even get rewarded for safe driving by participating in RightTrack. RightTrack runs in the background and automatically captures driving information using sensors.

We’re here for what you need, take care of what’s important, quickly and easily

● Access and download digital ID cards
● Get to know your coverages and receive customized recommendations
● Save money with our safe driving program (in most states)

We’re here when you need it most, find on-the-go help in the moments that matter

● Tap to call for Roadside Assistance
● File a claim, get real-time status updates, and contact your Claims Representative
● Upload pictures of damage and get a repair estimate quickly
● Schedule a damage review or request a rental vehicle
● View estimates, track repairs, and review claims payments

Permissions needed for RightTrack users

● RightTrack uses foreground services to enhance user safety, ensure accurate trip recording, and provide valuable feedback to the user regarding their driving behavior. It's essential for detecting when you start a drive and to accurately log the route taken, driving behavior, and other relevant metrics.
● The service is activated when you begin driving. This is detected through user interaction with the app and/or automatic detection algorithms that recognize driving activity.
● RightTrack collects data such as speed, acceleration, braking, and route information, which are needed for assessing driving behavior and providing feedback for safer driving practices.
